title: *PATREON PREVIEW* The Rent Is Too Damn High Pt. II with Chris Wallace
description:
This week’s entrée into high society conveniently continues behind the paywall for only the uppermost crust and biggest gang with Mr. Porter’s Chris Wallace, an extremely beautiful and thoughtful man. Mind your manners because it’s time for the filet and gratin as Chris and the boys nosh on Throwing Fits being the ISIS of Menswear, penetrating the luxury market, post-COVID consumer behavior, cutting your own hair, his proudest moment as a writer, being a step behind Tom Brady, surviving modeling, the best selling brand on Mr. Porter, the IG Live playbook, grounded jetsetter-onset depression, the art of regression, rent strike temptation, escalating levels of horniness and much more on this Patreon-exclusive episode of The Only Podcast That Matters™.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
